> **NOTE:** Available in v1.121.0+.

## Import


ECS Key Pair Attachment can be imported using the id, e.g.

```sh
 $ pulumi import alicloud:ecs/ecsKeyPairAttachment:EcsKeyPairAttachment example <key_pair_name>:<instance_ids>
```
